listening to you.

528
00:43:26.862 --> 00:43:28.586
and it never ever
will listen to you

529
00:43:28.689 --> 00:43:31.310
if there is nobody left
to stand trial for any of this.

530
00:43:31.413 --> 00:43:33.275
Please! Please!

531
00:43:35.758 --> 00:43:37.655
I want you to stop.

532
00:43:42.448 --> 00:43:43.448
Please.

533
00:43:46.724 --> 00:43:48.689
Stop.
I want you to stop.

534
00:43:54.517 --> 00:43:55.724
OK.

535
00:43:57.551 --> 00:44:00.344
OK. OK.

536
00:44:00.827 --> 00:44:02.206
Fuck!

537
00:44:17.862 --> 00:44:21.137
Ah. There you are.

538
00:44:21.241 --> 00:44:22.448
Don't talk to her!

539
00:44:24.482 --> 00:44:26.000
Why am I still alive?

540
00:44:27.448 --> 00:44:29.862
'Cause. you're
my favourite. silly rabbit.

541
00:44:31.172 --> 00:44:33.517
My Catherine was always
jealous of you.

542
00:44:34.413 --> 00:44:35.724
So canny. So clever.

543
00:44:35.827 --> 00:44:37.103
More headstrong
than the others.

544
00:44:37.689 --> 00:44:39.310
My best girl.

545
00:44:40.655 --> 00:44:42.241
I could have
kept you safe here.

546
00:44:42.344 --> 00:44:43.551
all to myself.

547
00:44:44.103 --> 00:44:45.586
No monsters
under the bed.

548
00:44:45.689 --> 00:44:47.137
Just us.

549
00:44:49.344 --> 00:44:50.862
It's not over yet.

550
00:44:51.655 --> 00:44:52.827
There's still time.

551
00:44:54.241 --> 00:44:56.206
I still think about you.

552
00:44:56.310 --> 00:44:57.793
Shut up.

553
00:44:58.517 --> 00:45:00.517
Oh. darling.

554
00:45:02.551 --> 00:45:04.103
It's the natural order.

555
00:45:04.448 --> 00:45:06.172
Shut the fuck up.

556
00:45:06.758 --> 00:45:08.103
There's no use fighting it.

557
00:45:08.758 --> 00:45:10.482
For all the hoping
and wishing

558
00:45:10.586 --> 00:45:12.620
that it shouldn't have
happened to you.

559
00:45:13.965 --> 00:45:15.793
Little boys
are made to fight.

560
00:45:15.896 --> 00:45:17.241
And little girls

561
00:45:18.172 --> 00:45:19.275
are made to fuck.

562
00:45:22.655 --> 00:45:24.344
You might
resist that order.

563
00:45:25.310 --> 00:45:27.034
but that was your destiny.

564
00:45:29.275 --> 00:45:31.413
Just like it was
Madeleine's destiny.

565
00:45:37.965 --> 00:45:39.793
It was like
having you back again.

566
00:45:52.241 --> 00:45:54.103
Oh. no! Oh. no!

567
00:45:54.206 --> 00:45:55.482
No! Oh. no. no!

568
00:45:57.344 --> 00:45:59.034
Shit!

569
00:45:59.793 --> 00:46:01.206
Your leg!

570
00:46:01.310 --> 00:46:03.000
Just stay still.
don't move.

571
00:46:03.689 --> 00:46:06.896
No. no. no.

572
00:46:16.241 --> 00:46:19.758
Don't leave me.

573
00:46:24.758 --> 00:46:25.793
Go.

574
00:46:27.758 --> 00:46:28.965
Go.

575
00:46:36.068 --> 00:46:37.034
I'm sorry.

576
00:46:40.896 --> 00:46:42.206
I'm sorry.

577
00:46:47.206 --> 00:46:49.172
♪ melancholic music playing

578
00:47:00.137 --> 00:47:03.034
It's not often in
life we can feel a page turn.

579
00:47:04.620 --> 00:47:06.896
<i>An old chapter ending
and a new one beginning.</i>

580
00:47:09.172 --> 00:47:11.689
<i>Where you can see
your world shifting.</i>

581
00:47:13.551 --> 00:47:15.068
<i>Feel your heart breaking.</i>

582
00:47:18.931 --> 00:47:21.206
<i>Sometimes I think about
where she might be.</i>

583
00:47:25.655 --> 00:47:27.655
<i>Sometimes. I don't
think of her at all.</i>

584
00:47:34.000 --> 00:47:37.137
<i>Sometimes I close my eyes.
and she's right there.</i>

585
00:47:38.344 --> 00:47:39.620
<i>They both are.</i>

586
00:47:42.931 --> 00:47:44.000
<i>But I love them.</i>

587
00:47:47.000 --> 00:47:48.137
<i>Both of them.</i>

588
00:47:51.862 --> 00:47:54.379
<i>My love for them was
as endless as the sea.</i>

589
00:48:03.620 --> 00:48:07.034
<i>♪ Rock-a-bye. baby
on the tree top ♪</i>

590
00:48:07.137 --> 00:48:08.310
<i>♪ On the tree top</i>

591
00:48:08.413 --> 00:48:11.620
<i>♪ When the wind blows
the cradle will rock ♪</i>

592
00:48:11.724 --> 00:48:12.965
<i>♪ It will rock</i>

593
00:48:13.068 --> 00:48:16.344
<i>♪ When the bough breaks
the cradle will fall ♪</i>

594
00:48:17.586 --> 00:48:22.206
<i>♪ And down will come baby
cradle and all ♪</i>

